Power Finance’s Borrowing Costs Rose 100 Basis Points

-- B y   K a r t i k a y   M e h r o t r a
-- 
2011-07-18T09:57:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-18/power-finance-s-borrowing-costs-rose-100-basis-points-correct-.html
Power Finance Corp.’s average
lending rate rose 100 basis points this year to as high as 13.5
percent, Chairman Satnam Singh told reporters in  New Delhi  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
